3f:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":"Roofers face a double threat: winter storms create emergency demand, but they're physically unable to answer while working at height. A single missed storm damage call can cost £2,000-8,000 in lost work."}]
40:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":["Storm season (October-January) accounts for 61% of annual losses. One roofer we interviewed ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/blog/i-lost-4000-in-one-storm-season-then-ai-answered-my-phone-tom-the-roofer","className":"text-[var(--katie-blue)] hover:underline","children":"lost £4,000 in a single storm"}]," because he was up a ladder when calls came in."]}]
