46:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-white","children":"June-August: £765K lost"}]," (ironically, during \"quiet\" season)"]}]
47:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":["Here's the surprise: builders lose the most money in summer, not winter. Why? Because extension and renovation enquiries peak in spring/summer when homeowners plan projects. But builders are busiest on-site during these months and miss the enquiry calls. One builder ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/blog/i-was-missing-2000-extension-enquiries-every-month-then-i-tried-ai-steve-the-builder","className":"text-[var(--katie-blue)] hover:underline","children":"was missing £2,000 in extension enquiries every month"}],"."]}]
